reviewText: this dvd contains Hulk Boiling Point vol. 2 and Hulk/Wolverine: Six Hours. If your a Hulk fan or a Wolverine fan you should love this. 2 TPBs for cheaper than the price of one. what more chould you want.

This DVD is a two parter. The first is a Hulk alone story arc and the second half is the Hulk/Wolverine story. But both are awesome. This would make a great gift for any Hulk or Wolverine fan. The voice-overs, effects, and music set the tone that brings the printed comic as close to an animation film as you can get. I plan on collecting the whole digital comic book set.
